Text: "I have bought several of the Vitality canned dog food products and have found them all to be of good quality. The product looks more like a stew than a processed meat and it smells better. My Labrador is finicky and she appreciates this product better than most."
"Product arrived labeled as Jumbo Salted Peanuts...the peanuts were actually small sized unsalted. Not sure if this was an error or if the vendor intended to represent the product as Jumbo"."""

"These chips were tasty and crisp. A little more greasy than I had hoped, but I'll keep an eye on that for the next time I open a bag.""

column16: "If you are looking for the secret ingredient in Robitussin it is glycerol and all the generic versions I have tried are missing it. Without it, the cold medicine is cruel; it works but it tastes like plastic. You might as well take the plastic tags off a new shirt and chew on them to relieve your sore throat. The actual product tastes great and I always buy it when I'm sick."

Summary: "Great coffee maker for camping and hiking"
Text: "This is a great coffee maker for camping and hiking. The mesh filter works well, and the entire setup packs away nicely. The price was very reasonable for a quality product."
"I had to buy a little coffee pot for my desk and this is perfect for me. It's very portable and makes a great cup of coffee."
"This is the perfect size for making one serving of coffee. The coffee tastes great and stays hot. It's easy to clean and very portable."
"Love this little coffee maker! It makes a delicious cup, it's super simple, and it's great quality. I would definitely recommend this product."

"I have used this brand for over 10 years now. It is the very best toothbrush - cleans well between teeth and along the gumline. My dental hygienist always comments on how clean my teeth are. I highly recommend it!"
"This toothbrush is way too soft. It feels like brushing with a cloth. I like firm toothbrushes that actually clean your teeth. This one is useless."
